The paper deals with iris recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of periocular information, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and biometrics (cs.CR). The proposed framework involves adaptive distance measures, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
